column1: UI FUNCTIONAL TESTING
column29:
h2. Objective

This epic aims to implement functional testing for the user interface of the Flight Ticket Booking System.

[Batch 18 Group 7 all sheets.xlsx|https://cognizantonline-my.sharepoint.com/:x:/r/personal/2416667_cognizant_com/Documents/Batch%2018%20Group%207%20all%20sheets.xlsx?d=we1431870482d40989d225ffc2947623d&csf=1&web=1&e=y4fiiL]

h2. Context

The focus is on ensuring that all UI components function correctly within the system.

h2. Scope

* *Included*: All UI-related functional testing.
* *Not Included*: Backend testing or non-UI related functionalities.

h2. Success criteria

* All UI components pass functional tests.
* No critical bugs are found in the UI.
* User experience meets defined standards.

h2. Risks and dependencies

* Potential delays in testing due to UI changes.
* Dependencies on the development team for timely updates.

h2. Other information

N/A
